<div id="pages__home">
  <div class="pages__home__hero" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_url('bg-img/herobg.jpg', type: :image) %>);">
    <h1>Hãy tìm những quyển sách bạn yêu thích</h1>
    <p>Enter a book you like and the site will analyse our huge database of real readers' favorite books to provide book<br> recommendations and suggestions for what to read next.</p>
    <p>Start typing the title or the author of a book you like, and click on the link underneath which matches best.<br>If several similar results are shown, click the highest one.</p>
    <div class='search-box-container'>
